---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Bitrate Compare — Video File Size Calculator"
  description="Compare video bitrates, file sizes, storage yield, and upload time with a fast visual calculator built for quick learning."
>
  <div class="flex min-h-dvh flex-col">
    <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-white/10 bg-zinc-950/90 backdrop-blur light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-50/90">
      <div class="mx-auto flex min-h-13 w-full max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-4 py-2.5 sm:px-5">
        <div class="flex min-w-0 items-center gap-3">
          <div class="flex size-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-[0.45rem] bg-indigo-500 text-white shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/20">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="min-w-0">
            <span class="block truncate font-display text-sm font-bold tracking-[-0.01em] text-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-900">Bitrate Compare</span>
            <p class="mt-0.5 hidden text-[12px] text-zinc-400 sm:block light:text-zinc-500">See how bitrate changes file size, storage, and transfer time before you export or record.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
          <button
            id="themeToggle"
            class="inline-flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-white/10 text-zinc-400 transition hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-zinc-100 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:text-zinc-500 light:hover:border-zinc-300 light:hover:bg-zinc-100 light:hover:text-zinc-900"
            aria-label="Toggle theme"
            type="button"
          >
            <svg id="iconSun" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"></circle><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3"></line><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23"></line><line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64"></line><line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78"></line><line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"></line><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12"></line><line x1="4.22" y1="19.78" x2="5.64" y2="18.36"></line><line x1="18.36" y1="5.64" x2="19.78" y2="4.22"></line>
            </svg>
            <svg id="iconMoon" class="hidden" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1111.21 3 7 7 0 0021 12.79z"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <button
            id="shareConfig"
            class="inline-flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-white/10 text-zinc-400 transition hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-zinc-100 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:text-zinc-500 light:hover:border-zinc-300 light:hover:bg-zinc-100 light:hover:text-zinc-900"
            aria-label="Share configuration"
            type="button"
          >
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M4 12v8a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-8"></path><polyline points="16 6 12 2 8 6"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="15"></line>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main id="main-content" class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-6xl flex-1 flex-col gap-6 px-4 py-4 pb-10 sm:px-5" tabindex="-1">
      <section class="overflow-hidden rounded-[1.125rem] border border-white/10 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_left,rgba(99,102,241,0.18),transparent_34%),linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(31,31,35,0.95),rgba(17,17,19,1))] p-4 shadow-2xl light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_left,rgba(79,70,229,0.12),transparent_34%),linear-gradient(180deg,#ffffff,#f4f4f5)]">
        <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.2fr)_minmax(0,0.8fr)] lg:items-end">
          <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <span class="inline-flex min-h-7 items-center rounded-full bg-indigo-500/12 px-3 text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-indigo-300 light:bg-indigo-500/10 light:text-indigo-600">Visual bitrate learning</span>
            <h1 class="mt-4 max-w-[13ch] font-display text-[clamp(1.85rem,4vw,2.75rem)] leading-none font-semibold tracking-[-0.045em] text-white text-balance light:text-zinc-950">Compare bitrates and see the storage hit instantly.</h1>
            <p class="mt-4 max-w-[58ch] text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-300 light:text-zinc-600">Set a runtime, add a few bitrate options, and the site will show how much larger the files get, how much storage they need, and how long they take to move.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-1">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/4 p-3 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100">
              <span class="text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-indigo-300 light:text-indigo-600">What changes</span>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-300 light:text-zinc-600">Higher bitrate keeps more data, so file size rises linearly with runtime.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/4 p-3 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100">
              <span class="text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-indigo-300 light:text-indigo-600">How to use it</span>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-300 light:text-zinc-600">Start with common examples like 10, 25, 50, or 100 Mbps, then adjust rows in place.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/4 p-3 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100">
              <span class="text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-indigo-300 light:text-indigo-600">What to compare</span>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-300 light:text-zinc-600">Look for the smallest profile that still fits your quality target and transfer window.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="grid gap-6 xl:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.9fr)_minmax(0,1.1fr)]">
        <div class="rounded-[1.125rem] border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 p-4 shadow-lg light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-white">
          <div class="mb-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
            <span class="block text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-500">Duration</span>
            <span id="totalDuration" class="text-sm font-bold tabular-nums text-indigo-300 light:text-indigo-600">0s</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mb-3.5 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600">This runtime is applied to every bitrate profile in the comparison.</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2.5">
            <div>
              <label class="mb-1.5 block text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600" for="hours">Hours</label>
              <input id="hours" type="number" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-3 text-center text-base font-medium text-zinc-100 outline-none transition placeholder:text-zinc-500 focus:border-indigo-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 aria-invalid:border-rose-400 aria-invalid:ring-2 aria-invalid:ring-rose-500/20 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-900 light:placeholder:text-zinc-400" value="0" min="0" placeholder="0" inputmode="numeric" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="mb-1.5 block text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600" for="minutes">Minutes</label>
              <input id="minutes" type="number" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-3 text-center text-base font-medium text-zinc-100 outline-none transition placeholder:text-zinc-500 focus:border-indigo-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 aria-invalid:border-rose-400 aria-invalid:ring-2 aria-invalid:ring-rose-500/20 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-900 light:placeholder:text-zinc-400" value="10" min="0" placeholder="0" inputmode="numeric" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="mb-1.5 block text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600" for="seconds">Seconds</label>
              <input id="seconds" type="number" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-3 text-center text-base font-medium text-zinc-100 outline-none transition placeholder:text-zinc-500 focus:border-indigo-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 aria-invalid:border-rose-400 aria-invalid:ring-2 aria-invalid:ring-rose-500/20 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-900 light:placeholder:text-zinc-400" value="0" min="0" placeholder="0" inputmode="numeric" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <button class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-2 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-300 transition hover:border-indigo-400/40 hover:text-zinc-100 aria-pressed:border-indigo-400/60 aria-pressed:bg-indigo-500/15 aria-pressed:text-zinc-100 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-600 light:hover:border-indigo-300 light:hover:text-zinc-900 light:aria-pressed:border-indigo-300 light:aria-pressed:bg-indigo-50 light:aria-pressed:text-indigo-700" type="button" data-duration-preset="0,1,0" aria-pressed="false">1 min</button>
            <button class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-2 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-300 transition hover:border-indigo-400/40 hover:text-zinc-100 aria-pressed:border-indigo-400/60 aria-pressed:bg-indigo-500/15 aria-pressed:text-zinc-100 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-600 light:hover:border-indigo-300 light:hover:text-zinc-900 light:aria-pressed:border-indigo-300 light:aria-pressed:bg-indigo-50 light:aria-pressed:text-indigo-700" type="button" data-duration-preset="0,10,0" aria-pressed="true">10 min</button>
            <button class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-2 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-300 transition hover:border-indigo-400/40 hover:text-zinc-100 aria-pressed:border-indigo-400/60 aria-pressed:bg-indigo-500/15 aria-pressed:text-zinc-100 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-600 light:hover:border-indigo-300 light:hover:text-zinc-900 light:aria-pressed:border-indigo-300 light:aria-pressed:bg-indigo-50 light:aria-pressed:text-indigo-700" type="button" data-duration-preset="0,30,0" aria-pressed="false">30 min</button>
            <button class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-2 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-300 transition hover:border-indigo-400/40 hover:text-zinc-100 aria-pressed:border-indigo-400/60 aria-pressed:bg-indigo-500/15 aria-pressed:text-zinc-100 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-600 light:hover:border-indigo-300 light:hover:text-zinc-900 light:aria-pressed:border-indigo-300 light:aria-pressed:bg-indigo-50 light:aria-pressed:text-indigo-700" type="button" data-duration-preset="1,0,0" aria-pressed="false">1 hour</button>
          </div>
          <p id="durationHint" class="mt-2 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500">Pick a quick example or enter your exact runtime.</p>
        </div>

        <section class="rounded-[1.125rem] border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 p-4 shadow-lg light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-white">
          <div class="mb-2 flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
            <span class="block text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-500">Bitrate Profiles</span>
            <span class="max-w-32 text-right text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500 sm:max-w-none">Manual comparison first</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mb-3.5 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600">Add the bitrate options you want to compare. The lowest resulting file becomes the baseline in the table below.</p>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800/60 p-3.5 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-50">
            <div class="mb-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <span class="block text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-indigo-300 light:text-indigo-600">Quick Start</span>
                <p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600">One click adds common bitrate examples so you can learn the spread fast.</p>
              </div>
              <button id="addStarterSet" class="inline-flex min-h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-500 px-3.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-indigo-400 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400" type="button">Add Starter Set</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <button class="min-h-10 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 px-3.5 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-indigo-400/50 hover:bg-indigo-500/10 hover:text-white focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-white light:text-zinc-700 light:hover:border-indigo-300 light:hover:text-zinc-900" type="button" data-starter-bitrate="10">10 Mbps</button>
              <button class="min-h-10 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 px-3.5 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-indigo-400/50 hover:bg-indigo-500/10 hover:text-white focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-white light:text-zinc-700 light:hover:border-indigo-300 light:hover:text-zinc-900" type="button" data-starter-bitrate="25">25 Mbps</button>
              <button class="min-h-10 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 px-3.5 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-indigo-400/50 hover:bg-indigo-500/10 hover:text-white focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-white light:text-zinc-700 light:hover:border-indigo-300 light:hover:text-zinc-900" type="button" data-starter-bitrate="50">50 Mbps</button>
              <button class="min-h-10 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 px-3.5 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-indigo-400/50 hover:bg-indigo-500/10 hover:text-white focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-white light:text-zinc-700 light:hover:border-indigo-300 light:hover:text-zinc-900" type="button" data-starter-bitrate="100">100 Mbps</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-3 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800/30 p-3.5 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-50">
            <div class="mb-2 flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
              <span class="block text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-zinc-300 light:text-zinc-700">Add a custom bitrate</span>
              <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500">Editable after adding</span>
            </div>
            <div id="manualMode" class="space-y-2.5" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="modeManualBtn">
              <div class="grid gap-2.5 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(0,170px)_auto]">
                <div>
                  <label class="mb-1.5 block text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600" for="manualName">Profile Name</label>
                  <input id="manualName" type="text" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-3 text-base font-medium text-zinc-100 outline-none transition placeholder:text-zinc-500 focus:border-indigo-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-900 light:placeholder:text-zinc-400" placeholder="Optional label" autocomplete="off" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label class="mb-1.5 block text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600" for="manualBitrate">Bitrate (Mbps)</label>
                  <input id="manualBitrate" type="number" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-3 text-base font-medium text-zinc-100 outline-none transition placeholder:text-zinc-500 focus:border-indigo-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 aria-invalid:border-rose-400 aria-invalid:ring-2 aria-invalid:ring-rose-500/20 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-900 light:placeholder:text-zinc-400" value="25" min="1" step="0.1" inputmode="decimal" />
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-end">
                  <button id="addManualProfile" class="inline-flex min-h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-500 px-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-indigo-400 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400" type="button">Add Profile</button>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2" aria-label="Common bitrate presets">
                <button class="min-h-10 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3.5 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 transition hover:border-indigo-400/50 hover:bg-indigo-500/10 hover:text-zinc-100 aria-pressed:border-indigo-400/60 aria-pressed:bg-indigo-500/15 aria-pressed:text-zinc-100 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-600 light:hover:bg-indigo-50 light:hover:text-indigo-700 light:aria-pressed:border-indigo-300 light:aria-pressed:bg-indigo-50 light:aria-pressed:text-indigo-700" type="button" data-bitrate-chip="10" aria-pressed="false">10 Mbps</button>
                <button class="min-h-10 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3.5 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 transition hover:border-indigo-400/50 hover:bg-indigo-500/10 hover:text-zinc-100 aria-pressed:border-indigo-400/60 aria-pressed:bg-indigo-500/15 aria-pressed:text-zinc-100 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-600 light:hover:bg-indigo-50 light:hover:text-indigo-700 light:aria-pressed:border-indigo-300 light:aria-pressed:bg-indigo-50 light:aria-pressed:text-indigo-700" type="button" data-bitrate-chip="25" aria-pressed="true">25 Mbps</button>
                <button class="min-h-10 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3.5 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 transition hover:border-indigo-400/50 hover:bg-indigo-500/10 hover:text-zinc-100 aria-pressed:border-indigo-400/60 aria-pressed:bg-indigo-500/15 aria-pressed:text-zinc-100 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-600 light:hover:bg-indigo-50 light:hover:text-indigo-700 light:aria-pressed:border-indigo-300 light:aria-pressed:bg-indigo-50 light:aria-pressed:text-indigo-700" type="button" data-bitrate-chip="50" aria-pressed="false">50 Mbps</button>
                <button class="min-h-10 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3.5 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 transition hover:border-indigo-400/50 hover:bg-indigo-500/10 hover:text-zinc-100 aria-pressed:border-indigo-400/60 aria-pressed:bg-indigo-500/15 aria-pressed:text-zinc-100 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-600 light:hover:bg-indigo-50 light:hover:text-indigo-700 light:aria-pressed:border-indigo-300 light:aria-pressed:bg-indigo-50 light:aria-pressed:text-indigo-700" type="button" data-bitrate-chip="100" aria-pressed="false">100 Mbps</button>
              </div>
              <p id="manualProfileHelp" class="mt-1.5 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500">Tip: leave the name blank to auto-label the row. You can still rename and fine-tune it in the table.</p>
              <p id="manualValidation" class="mt-1.5 min-h-[18px] text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 data-[state=warning]:text-amber-400 data-[state=error]:text-rose-400 data-[state=success]:text-emerald-400 light:text-zinc-500 light:data-[state=warning]:text-amber-600 light:data-[state=error]:text-rose-600 light:data-[state=success]:text-emerald-600" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <section class="mt-3 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800/20 px-3.5 py-3 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-50">
            <div class="mb-3 flex items-center">
              <span class="block text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500">Advanced options</span>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-3 light:border-zinc-200">
                <div class="mb-2 flex rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 p-[3px] light:bg-zinc-100" role="tablist" aria-label="Add profile mode">
                  <button id="modeManualBtn" class="flex-1 rounded-md px-3 py-3 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-100 shadow-sm transition aria-selected:bg-zinc-900 aria-selected:text-zinc-100 aria-selected:shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] light:text-zinc-500 light:aria-selected:bg-white light:aria-selected:text-zinc-900" type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="manualMode">Manual</button>
                  <button id="modeCameraBtn" class="flex-1 rounded-md px-3 py-3 text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-500 transition aria-selected:bg-zinc-900 aria-selected:text-zinc-100 aria-selected:shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] light:text-zinc-500 light:aria-selected:bg-white light:aria-selected:text-zinc-900" type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="cameraMode">Camera Preset</button>
                </div>
                <div id="cameraMode" class="hidden space-y-2.5" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="modeCameraBtn">
                  <p class="text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600">Use this only if you want to pull in a known camera bitrate instead of typing one manually.</p>
                  <div>
                    <label class="mb-1.5 block text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600" for="cameraSelect">Camera</label>
                    <div class="relative" data-select-wrap>
                      <select id="cameraSelect" class="w-full appearance-none rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-3 pr-10 text-base font-medium text-zinc-100 outline-none transition focus:border-indigo-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-900">
                        <option value="">Choose camera...</option>
                      </select>
                      <span class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 right-3 flex items-center text-zinc-500">
                        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" /></svg>
                      </span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <label class="mb-1.5 block text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600" for="codecSelect">Codec / Profile</label>
                    <div class="relative hidden" data-select-wrap>
                      <select id="codecSelect" class="w-full appearance-none rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-3 pr-10 text-base font-medium text-zinc-100 outline-none transition focus:border-indigo-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-900">
                        <option value="">Choose codec / bitrate...</option>
                      </select>
                      <span class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 right-3 flex items-center text-zinc-500">
                        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" /></svg>
                      </span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <button id="addCameraProfile" class="hidden min-h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-zinc-100 px-4 text-base font-semibold text-zinc-900 transition hover:bg-white focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:bg-zinc-900 light:text-white light:hover:bg-zinc-800" type="button">Add Camera Profile</button>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-3 light:border-zinc-200">
                <div class="mb-2 flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
                  <span class="block text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-500">Assumptions</span>
                  <span class="max-w-32 text-right text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500 sm:max-w-none">Storage and transfer</span>
                </div>
                <div class="grid gap-2.5 md:grid-cols-3">
                  <div>
                    <label class="mb-1.5 block text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600" for="availableStorage">Available Storage (GB)</label>
                    <input id="availableStorage" name="availableStorage" type="number" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-3 text-base font-medium text-zinc-100 outline-none transition placeholder:text-zinc-500 focus:border-indigo-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 aria-invalid:border-rose-400 aria-invalid:ring-2 aria-invalid:ring-rose-500/20 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-900 light:placeholder:text-zinc-400" value="500" min="0" step="1" inputmode="numeric" />
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <label class="mb-1.5 block text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600" for="costPerTB">Media Cost ($/TB)</label>
                    <input id="costPerTB" name="costPerTB" type="number" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-3 text-base font-medium text-zinc-100 outline-none transition placeholder:text-zinc-500 focus:border-indigo-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 aria-invalid:border-rose-400 aria-invalid:ring-2 aria-invalid:ring-rose-500/20 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-900 light:placeholder:text-zinc-400" value="20" min="0" step="0.01" inputmode="decimal" />
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <label class="mb-1.5 block text-[12px] font-semibold text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600" for="customSpeed">Custom Upload Speed (Mbps)</label>
                    <input id="customSpeed" name="customSpeed" type="number" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-3 text-base font-medium text-zinc-100 outline-none transition placeholder:text-zinc-500 focus:border-indigo-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 aria-invalid:border-rose-400 aria-invalid:ring-2 aria-invalid:ring-rose-500/20 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-900 light:placeholder:text-zinc-400" value="50" min="1" step="1" inputmode="numeric" />
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p id="settingsStatus" class="mt-1.5 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500">Uses decimal GB/TB and megabits per second for transfer speed.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </section>
      </section>

        <section id="comparisonSection" class="hidden rounded-[1.125rem] border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 p-4 shadow-md light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-white">
          <div class="mb-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
            <div>
              <span class="block text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-500">Comparison Table <span id="profileCount" class="text-indigo-300 light:text-indigo-600">0</span></span>
              <p id="comparisonHint" class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500">Rows are sorted from smallest to largest file. The smallest file is the baseline.</p>
            </div>
            <button id="clearAll" class="rounded-md px-2 py-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-zinc-500 transition hover:bg-rose-500/8 hover:text-rose-400 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 light:hover:bg-rose-50 light:hover:text-rose-600" type="button">Clear all</button>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-800/50 px-3.5 py-3 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-300 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-50 light:text-zinc-600">
            Higher bitrate creates proportionally larger files at the same duration. Use the delta column to see how far each option moves from the most storage-efficient profile.
          </div>
          <div class="-mx-4 mt-2 overflow-x-auto px-4 [scrollbar-width:thin]">
            <table class="w-full min-w-[760px] border-collapse text-left text-xs">
              <caption class="sr-only">Bitrate comparison table</caption>
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th class="pr-2 pb-2 text-[12px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500" scope="col">Profile</th>
                  <th class="pr-2 pb-2 text-[12px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500" scope="col">Bitrate</th>
                  <th class="pr-2 pb-2 text-[12px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500" scope="col">Est. Size</th>
                  <th class="pr-2 pb-2 text-[12px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500" scope="col">Delta vs Baseline</th>
                  <th class="pr-2 pb-2 text-[12px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500" scope="col">Media Cost</th>
                  <th class="pr-0 pb-2 text-[12px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500" scope="col">Actions</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody id="profilesContainer">
                <tr class="sr-only">
                  <td colspan="6">No profiles added yet.</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <p id="profilesEmpty" class="mt-3 rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-white/10 bg-zinc-800/70 p-3.5 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 data-[state=warning]:text-amber-400 data-[state=error]:text-rose-400 data-[state=success]:text-emerald-400 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-zinc-100 light:text-zinc-500 light:data-[state=warning]:text-amber-600 light:data-[state=error]:text-rose-600 light:data-[state=success]:text-emerald-600">No profiles yet. Add a bitrate profile to compare file size, upload time, and storage yield.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="chartSection" class="hidden rounded-[1.125rem] border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 p-4 shadow-md light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-white">
          <div class="mb-2 flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
            <span class="block text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-500">Size Comparison</span>
            <span class="max-w-32 text-right text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500 sm:max-w-none">Largest file sets the scale</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mb-3.5 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600">This chart makes the file-size jump easy to scan at a glance.</p>
          <div id="barChart" class="mt-2"></div>
        </section>

        <section id="uploadSection" class="hidden rounded-[1.125rem] border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 p-4 shadow-md light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-white">
          <div class="mb-2 flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
            <span class="block text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-500">Upload Estimates</span>
            <span class="max-w-28 text-right text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500 sm:max-w-none">Based on full file size</span>
          </div>
          <p class="helper-text section-intro">Check whether each file can clear your transfer window at common upload speeds.</p>
          <div class="upload-legend" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="upload-legend-item"><span class="upload-legend-swatch upload-legend-swatch-fast"></span>Fast</span>
            <span class="upload-legend-item"><span class="upload-legend-swatch upload-legend-swatch-mid"></span>Moderate</span>
            <span class="upload-legend-item"><span class="upload-legend-swatch upload-legend-swatch-slow"></span>Slow</span>
            <span class="upload-legend-item"><span class="upload-legend-swatch upload-legend-swatch-very-slow"></span>Very slow</span>
          </div>
          <div class="table-scroll upload-heatmap-scroll">
            <div class="upload-heatmap" role="table" aria-label="Upload estimate heatmap">
              <div class="upload-heatmap-head" role="rowgroup">
                <div class="upload-heatmap-row upload-heatmap-row-head" role="row">
                  <div class="upload-heatmap-cell upload-heatmap-cell-label" role="columnheader">Profile</div>
                  <div class="upload-heatmap-cell upload-heatmap-cell-size" role="columnheader">Size</div>
                  <div class="upload-heatmap-cell upload-heatmap-cell-speed" role="columnheader">20M</div>
                  <div class="upload-heatmap-cell upload-heatmap-cell-speed" role="columnheader">100M</div>
                  <div class="upload-heatmap-cell upload-heatmap-cell-speed" role="columnheader">1G</div>
                  <div class="upload-heatmap-cell upload-heatmap-cell-speed" role="columnheader">10G</div>
                  <div class="upload-heatmap-cell upload-heatmap-cell-speed" role="columnheader" id="customSpeedHeader">50M</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div id="uploadTable" class="upload-heatmap-body" role="rowgroup">
                <div class="upload-heatmap-empty sr-only">Add profiles to see upload estimates.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="yieldSection" class="hidden rounded-[1.125rem] border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 p-4 shadow-md light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-white">
          <div class="mb-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
            <div>
              <span class="block text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-500">Storage Yield</span>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 light:text-zinc-500">Estimated total recording time each profile gets from the storage value above.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold tabular-nums text-zinc-400 light:text-zinc-600" id="yieldStorageLabel">500 GB</span>
          </div>
          <div id="capacityResults" class="flex flex-col gap-1"></div>
        </section>
      </main>

      <footer class="px-4 py-4 text-center text-[12px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.06em] text-zinc-600 light:text-zinc-400">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-3 gap-y-1">
          <span>Bitrate Compare &bull; 2025</span>
          <a
            href="https://youtube.com/@alphabravomedia"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
            class="transition hover:text-zinc-300 light:hover:text-zinc-700"
          >
            YouTube
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/Today20092/video-bitrate-site"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
            class="transition hover:text-zinc-300 light:hover:text-zinc-700"
          >
            GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </footer>

      <div id="toast" class="pointer-events-none fixed right-4 bottom-4 translate-y-16 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium text-zinc-100 opacity-0 shadow-xl transition duration-200 data-[visible=true]:translate-y-0 data-[visible=true]:opacity-100 light:border-zinc-200 light:bg-white light:text-zinc-900" data-visible="false" aria-live="polite">Link copied to clipboard</div>
    </div>

    <script>
      import '../scripts/app.js';
    </script>
  </div>
</Layout>
